snippet.title: CSO2 | Counter-Strike Online 2 - Big City PVE / PVP Walkthrough
snippet.description:
This video showcases walkthrough of "Big City: PVE" and "Big City: PVP" gamemodes in Counter-Strike Online 2. Recorded on the Global Server from the point of view of ADVABonnie.

Big City gamemodes were added to the game in the latest update and available exclusively on the Global Server.

First and the only one CSO2 server to feature Big City: https://cso2.wohlnet.ru
Discord: https://discord.gg/NXYypCQ
VK: https://vk.com/cso2.global

0:00 - Introduction
0:59 - Big City: PVE
56:47 - Big City: PVP
